{"tid":1858071,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"黃埔花園睇樓量急挫　議幅漸擴","createTime":"2020-02-02T13:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T16:31:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c5fa915205b02054028c694360816867ae0adc42","tid":1858071,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200201/_2020020122503165657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200201%2F_2020020122503165657.jpg&h=c255aa60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃埔花園睇樓量急挫 ，議幅漸擴。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐本港，疫情持續升溫，部分確診患者居住的「失守屋苑」，睇樓量即時急挫，其中新近有住客確診新型肺炎的紅磡黃埔花園，睇樓量即時急挫，太陽物業分行經理宏惠強表示，有關事件出現後，不少業主即時封盤，而整體預約睇樓量按周跌逾六成，其中患者居住的11期，更沒有任何準買家睇樓。<br />\n<br />\n美聯區域聯席董事殷勒麟表示，黃埔花園成「失守屋苑」後，有部分業主增時擴大議價空間，由原先的約5%，增至約10%。而屋苑管理處則要求代理帶客睇樓時全程一定要帶口罩，否則不可進入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/pp/1692309/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB-%E9%BB%83%E5%9F%94%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E7%9D%87%E6%A8%93%E9%87%8F%E6%80%A5%E6%8C%AB-%E8%AD%B0%E5%B9%85%E6%BC%B8%E6%93%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fpp%2F1692309%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25BA%25AB-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259F%2594%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%258C%25AB-%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B9%2585%25E6%25BC%25B8%25E6%2593%25B4&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=662dbf07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fpp%2F1692309%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25BA%25AB-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259F%2594%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%259D%2587%25E